results.title: Live Laugh Love Sign / Wine Bottle Lights / Live Laugh Love Decor / Live Laugh Love Home Decor / Friend Birthday Gift
results.description:
Live Laugh Love Wine Bottle Lights 

Bottle Lights Info:
1.	The lights are LED starry lights from an artificial wine cork. They take 1 AAA battery (the battery is not included). 
2.	The top of the artificial wine cork is removed by twisting to add/change the battery. Simply twist the top of the cork back on after adding/changing the battery.  To turn the lights on twist the top of the cork tightly to the direction the cap indicates. When turning the lights off simply twist the cork to the direction the cap indicates. 
3.	Make sure that the spring in the detachable part of the cork is tightly inserted.
4.	The detachable portion of the artificial wine cork can be left on the cork while the lights are turned off. 
5.	Since it is artificial and also a battery pack, it sits loosely in the top of the wine bottle yet tightly enough that when the bottle is sitting for display it sits nicely. 
6.	These lights completes the look of a wine bottle although the “cork” is artificial. 

The wording is made from a permanent vinyl.

All bottles are 750mL clear, recycled bottles. Some of the bottle have different hues to them such as a darker clear or a blueish clear.

Bottle Finish: 
All wine bottles are upcycled. The bottles go through a thorough cleaning process, then the labels are removed, and then the bottles are cleaned again and go through a drying process. 
Please keep in mind that these are all recycled wine bottles and they are thoroughly cleaned. If there are any marks on the bottle it is from the recycling and cleaning process. However they will be hardly noticeable. 

The bottles are lightly frosted so that the wording and images are clear to read and view when the lights are turned both off and on.  

Lightly Frosted Info:
1.	The lightly frosted finish helps the image on the bottle be more visible in some cases. 
2.	Please take care not to have the bottle hit against any rough surfaces as it can leave marks in the frosting.
3.	When handling the bottle, hold the bottle from the stem. If you touch the frosting parts of the bottle, fingerprints can be left visible on the frosting.

results.description:
Live Laugh Love?  Fuck right off!  Express your distaste at the sickly-sweet saying with a variety of alternatives (including one for the Whovians!).

You will receive three files:
• A PDF 'How to Cross Stitch' guide
• A PDF file featuring full colour charts of all pattern variations.

Stitches required:

You will need:
• Fabric (we recommend white 14 count Aida cloth)
• Embroidery thread / floss (pattern lists DMC brand colour codes but you can use any type)

results.title: Wrap Around Double Layer Black  White Leather Inspirational Bracelet
results.description:
Wrap Around Double Layer Black & White Leather Inspirational Bracelet

Chrissie C has teamed up a genuine black braided 4mm leather, with a flat white coloured leather.

The flat leather is stamp etched with the mantra "Laugh Every Day, Love Beyond Words, Live Every Moment"

We love this positive uplifting inspirational quote here at the EWE project.

This is a totally unisex bracelet and looks cool on the small or large wrist as its made to measure for you.

Your bracelet is finished with a stainless steel bayonet interlocking clasp.  We love stainless steel here at the EWE project as it does not fade or tarnish like other metals.

Your bracelet will be crafted with love and passion and will come in a velvet gift pouch.

At time of order, please also do advise your actual wrist size so we can ensure the perfect fit for you.

 
SIZING


To ensure you get the perfect fit for your styling...

1: Measure your wrist with a flexible tape, strip of paper or piece of string , where you would normally wear the bracelet. The tape should be firm around the wrist but not tight.

 2: If you are using a strip of paper or cord, mark your size with a pen or pencil then use a ruler to measure the length. That would be your exact wrist size.

 3: To find your bracelet size,  

Examples showing a looser comfort fit. (If you prefer a tighter and close  fit, please message me at time of order and i will craft slightly smaller)

1. 15cm wrist (lady or small wrist)  may choose 55cm

(if you like a tighter fit please request this and i will craft to approx 53cm)

2.  18cm wrist may choose 65cm.

(if you like a tighter fit please request this and i will craft to approx 63cm)

3.  20cm wrist may choose 68cm

(if you like a tighter fit please request this and i will craft to approx 66cm)

4.  22cm wrist may choose 74cm

(if you like a tighter fit please request this and i will craft to approx 72 cm)

If you need help or need a size not shown please message me or leave me a note when placing you order.  

We can also craft in different colour leathers and styles, so please message me for different style and leather options.

CARE FOR YOUR LEATHER BRACELET

We advise with all leather products to avoid bathing/showering in them and avoid wearing whilst  swimming or engaging in water based activities to preserve the leather.
